WEBVTT

00:01.000 --> 00:02.334
               ♪

00:02.336 --> 00:04.136
        [birds chirping]

00:04.138 --> 00:09.508
   [gasping for air] Twilight?
    Can you slow down a bit?

00:09.510 --> 00:12.378
 Sorry, Spike. It's just Pinkie
    Pie, Rarity and Applejack

00:12.380 --> 00:14.513
   are getting back from their
    Seaward Shoals boat trip.

00:18.385 --> 00:21.053
 It's such a shame Rainbow Dash
  and Fluttershy had to miss it

00:21.055 --> 00:23.122
      for their Cloudsdale
     Flight School reunion.

00:23.124 --> 00:25.758
 Maybe the rest of us not going
    was for the best anyway.

00:25.760 --> 00:28.360
    I know the three of them
   were really looking forward

00:28.362 --> 00:30.629
to getting out of their element.

00:30.631 --> 00:32.464
  Getting out of their element?

00:32.466 --> 00:35.167
      I think they all just
  wanted to try something new.

00:35.169 --> 00:37.436
  Huh. I guess a boat
trip qualifies as that.

00:37.438 --> 00:39.304
My only worry is
they'll be so excited,

00:39.306 --> 00:42.174
and I'll miss some
of the details.

00:42.176 --> 00:44.710
Just to be safe, I may
need you to take notes.

00:44.712 --> 00:46.278
           Uh, right.

00:46.280 --> 00:49.381
   [train chugging]

00:49.383 --> 00:51.183
         [steam hisses]

00:56.523 --> 00:58.290
      So how was the trip?

